Package: ambient-brightness
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.6), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, systemd
Recommends: python3-opencv, python3-numpy
Maintainer: linux-ambient <https://github.com/jjermany/linux-ambient>
Homepage: https://github.com/jjermany/linux-ambient
Description: Automatic screen brightness adjustment for Linux
 Ambient Brightness Control provides automatic screen brightness adjustment
 using ambient light sensors or camera, similar to smartphones and macOS.
 .
 Features:
  - Graphical User Interface with real-time monitoring
  - System Tray Integration
  - Dual sensor support (ALS or camera fallback)
  - Smart brightness algorithm
  - Runs as user systemd service
  - No root access needed for normal operation
